{"type":"element","name":"section","elements":[{"type":"element","name":"rac_column_heds_with_rule","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Revisit the Concept Question"}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"As we read the Big Chart, let’s think about how it connects to this week’s Concept Question: What makes us who we are?"}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_column_heds_with_rule","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Close-Read: Connect to All About Me"}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_body-text","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Read aloud the teacher text on the Big Chart. Then use these prompts to read and discuss the poster together. "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_body-text","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Use Equity Sticks during reading to choose children to take turns responding. "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_d-hed_page_number","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Title"}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"The title of this poster is “I like to . . .” Who can point to the words? Who can point to the pictures? "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_d-hed_page_number","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"read a book"}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Point to the boy with the book. The boy says, “I like to read a book.” I think the boy is reading about dinosaurs. What do you think he is reading about? "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_d-hed_page_number","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"play catch"}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_teacher-talk_blue","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Point to the girl with the red ball. The girl says, “I like to play catch.” I’ll pretend to throw a ball and you catch it. "}]},{"type":"element","name":"rac_hilight_teacher_inst_new","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Revisit "},{"type":"element","name":"rac_highlight_teacher_inst_Italic","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"catch"}